    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Groups of wild or domestic mammals of one species that remain together, specifically applied to horses, zebra, oxen, antelope, cattle, camels, buffalo, elephants, deer, swine, whales, or certain other species.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
